Technical Analysis

Tech Stack
	Frontend : JSP, CSS, JS
	Backend : Sring Boot, Java 11
	Database : MySQL
	Server: Embedded Tomcat 

Flow of Application - chart

UI(Responsive)

First Name:
Required
Minimum length: 2, Maximum length: 50
Only alphabets and spaces allowed
Special characters or numbers trigger an error
Prevent pasting more than maximum characters
Validate on onblur event

Last Name:
Required
Minimum length: 2, Maximum length: 50
Only alphabets and spaces allowed
Special characters or numbers trigger an error
Prevent pasting more than maximum characters
Validate on onblur event

Date of Birth (DOB):
Required
Age must be between 18 and 110 years
Validate on onblur event

Mobile:
Required
Maximum 10 digits
Only numeric characters allowed
Cannot start with 0
Must be unique (no duplicate numbers)
Validate on onblur event

Password:
Required
Encrypted
Minimum length: 8, Maximum length: 30
Must satisfy regex pattern (e.g., uppercase, lowercase, number, special character)
No spaces allowed
Prevent pasting beyond maximum length
Password toggle feature available
Validate on onblur event

Address 1:
Required
Maximum length allowed
Accept all characters

Address 2:
Optional
Maximum length same as Address 1
Accept all characters

Age:
Auto-calculated from DOB
Display only; cannot be manually entered
Shown during both edit and submission

Gender:
Required
Must select one option (radio buttons)

Email:
Required
Must be a valid email format
Must be unique (no duplicate emails)
Validate on onblur event



Valid then submit

Controller (@RestController) ----> RequestDTO validation ----> Service interface (CustomerService) ----> ServiceImpl (CustomerServiceImpl) ----> Repository (CustomerRepository) â†’ Database
Repository (CustomerRepository) ----> ResponseDTO ----> Controller ----> JSON Response ----> Client


RestController ---> EmployeeController
Service ----------> EmployeeService
ServiceImpl ------> EmployeeServiceImpl
DTO --------------> RequestDto and ResponceDto
Repository -------> EmployeeREpository
Entity -----------> Employee

RestApi go to frontend and access data


| Column Name     | Data Type                     | Constraints / Notes                                          |
| --------------- | ----------------------------- | ------------------------------------------------------------ |
| `id`            | LONG                          | Primary Key, Auto Increment                                  |
| `first_name`    | VARCHAR(50)                   | Required, min 2, max 50, alphabets and spaces only           |
| `last_name`     | VARCHAR(50)                   | Required, min 2, max 50, alphabets and spaces only           |
| `date_of_birth` | DATE                          | Required, age between 18 and 110                             |
| `mobile`        | VARCHAR(10)                   | Required, unique, only digits,	                         |
| `password`      | VARCHAR(255)                  | Required, min 8, max 30                                      |
| `address1`      | VARCHAR(255)                  | Required                                                     |
| `address2`      | VARCHAR(255)                  | Optional                                                     |
| `age`           | INT                           | Auto-calculated from DOB, cannot be manually edited          |
| `gender`        | VARCHAR(10)                   | Required, must select one option                             |
| `email`         | VARCHAR(100)                  | Required, unique, valid email format                         |
